{"tid":786402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]學 生 獨 立 聯 盟 再 次 驅 趕 大 嬸","createTime":"2018-08-20T01:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T04:28:01.000Z","uid":47359,"like":94,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a79390ecd544144b838d279edc9821a6198cafe2","tid":786402,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:45:28.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180818/bkn-20180818192757026-0818_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180818%2Fbkn-20180818192757026-0818_00822_001.html&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=891fdc25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180818/bkn-20180818192757026-0818_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n學獨聯fb page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/students.independence.union/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudents.independence.union%2F&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ea8d62e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/students.independence.union/</a><br />\n<br />\n旺角行人專用區「殺街」後，大媽表演團「曲終人未散」，轉場至尖沙咀天星碼頭繼續高歌。本土團體「學生獨立聯盟」今(18日)再次到海傍監察大媽，他們拉起一人高的「請勿行乞」標語巡視海傍，要求製造高分貝噪音的大媽表演團離開。<br />\n<br />\n有表演者在「學生獨立聯盟」到來前，已連忙收拾音響設備離開。天星碼頭今晚鮮有大媽團高歌，現場亦未有衝突情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n召集人陳家駒表示，不想因大媽團而令一個景點再度被封殺，聯盟會繼續密切監察尖沙咀情況。"},{"pid":"a77b28c957e81882d04cde654ab35bb9ea37c1a0","tid":786402,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b087f57a8d79227dadede96eaab080b2bd661385","tid":786402,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0683ea5141ede4fa33a201fb71012d2214b77c4",